#compdef brew
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Description
# -----------
#
#  Completion script for brew (https://github.com/mxcl/homebrew).
#
#  Source: https://github.com/mxcl/homebrew/blob/master/Library/Contributions/brew_zsh_completion.zsh
#
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Authors
# -------
#
